mlx (expm1f device routine)
---------------------------

The fused xIELU Metal kernel in
src/lib/mlxcel-core/cpp/mlx_cxx_kernels.cpp reproduces the device-side
expm1f routine from mlx/backend/metal/kernels/expm1f.h in MLX
(https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx), Copyright (c) Apple Inc., licensed
under the MIT License. The JIT metal_kernel preamble does not pull that
header in and Metal's <metal_math> provides no expm1, so the routine is
inlined verbatim (renamed) to keep the fused activation byte-identical to
the elementwise path that calls mlx::core::expm1. The MIT License text in
the section above (Copyright © 2023 Apple Inc.) covers this reuse.

